divs: Sighting Detailssitting outside this evening we saw a bright light. We see Planes and stars each night but this was neither. we went into the house and got the binoculars and went back to see if we could get a better look. well we did. Three sets of three lights sittting Diagonally. It is now 10:22PM and it is still there. It moves up and down in the sky but we still can't make out what it is. It is now starting to move Northwest. Can someone comfirm?
